author: National Geographic
description:
Paid content for @PepsiCo. Join National Geographic photographer Rena Effendi as she visits Iowa family farmer Wendy Johnson. Discover how Wendy's farm is beating the odds, building a resilient agricultural legacy beyond three generations with regenerative farming practices. See how PepsiCo is supporting sustainable farming, helping to strengthen rural communities, and helping local farmers thrive.
